file.name: ship_placements.yml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
description: Ship placement endpoint
tags:
  - name: ship-placements
consumes:
  - "application/json"
produces:
  - "application/json"
parameters:
  - in: body
    name: body
    required: true
    schema:
      type: object
      properties:
        horizontal_space_numbers:
          type: object
          example: {1: [2, 1, 2], 4: [1, 4, 1], 7: [1, 1, 1]}
        vertical_space_numbers:
          type: object
          example: {2: [1, 2, 4], 5: [1, 2, 3], 7: [3, 1, 1]}
responses:
    '200':
      description: List of seas with stationed ships
      schema:
        type: array
        items:
          type: array
    '400':
      description: Bad Request
    '500':
      description: Internal Server Error
